      "writtenOn": "2017-12-08T23:21:41Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Sigh, py24eva.\n\n$ python -c \u0027open(\"/\")\u0027\nTraceback (most recent call last):\n  File \"\u003cstring\u003e\", line 1, in \u003cmodule\u003e\nIOError: [Errno 21] Is a directory: \u0027/\u0027\n$ python -c \u0027open(\"fdsa\")\u0027\nTraceback (most recent call last):\n  File \"\u003cstring\u003e\", line 1, in \u003cmodule\u003e\nIOError: [Errno 2] No such file or directory: \u0027fdsa\u0027\n$ python3 -c \u0027open(\"/\")\u0027\nTraceback (most recent call last):\n  File \"\u003cstring\u003e\", line 1, in \u003cmodule\u003e\nIsADirectoryError: [Errno 21] Is a directory: \u0027/\u0027\n$ python3 -c \u0027open(\"fdsa\")\u0027\nTraceback (most recent call last):\n  File \"\u003cstring\u003e\", line 1, in \u003cmodule\u003e\nFileNotFoundError: [Errno 2] No such file or directory: \u0027fdsa\u0027\n\n(No action required, not worth worrying about build.ninja being a directory or unreadable or whatever weird thing might come up.)",
      "range": {
